{"TopicId":134871,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Eve Escaper","CreatedByName":"gilflo","CreatedById":62881,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-24T18:50:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"gilflo","CreatedById":62881,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-24T18:50:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey guys\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI built an odd machine, a mix between a nuclear plane and a rocket to reach orbit. I hyper edited it on Eve.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe\u00A0nuclear engines of the plane brings up the whole thing at 13000m where the rocket is released. The top of the rocket can reach a 110 kms orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEve escaper can also be used to fly over Eve and is able to land.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI got some idea to de-orbit the thing and\u00A0descent on retrograde protected by tons of ablator.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I do not know is if it will support the transition between retrograde and prograde, once under 13000m.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis thing is \u0022fragile\u0022 and very tricky to pilot. I only pilot it through pilot assistant because it looks like you are always on the top of a pin when flying under 5000m over Eve.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLanding must be a kiss if you do not want to destroy the 200T ship. I made some test flights and managed to land it near the sea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can sea that on a vid, take off is touchy - i used bank 0 on Pilot assistant and the gear suffered on landing, due to braking, but did not break. Since that I did some improvement.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTake off is much better, don\u0027t need to jump on Bank 0, and landing seems better with a pair of chutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/3u5Fj7DIOY0?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.hostingpics.net/viewer.php?id=184135screenshot261.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022184135screenshot261.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img15.hostingpics.net/pics/184135screenshot261.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.hostingpics.net/viewer.php?id=391504screenshot262.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022391504screenshot262.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img15.hostingpics.net/pics/391504screenshot262.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.hostingpics.net/viewer.php?id=158788screenshot263.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022158788screenshot263.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img15.hostingpics.net/pics/158788screenshot263.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.hostingpics.net/viewer.php?id=405678screenshot265.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022405678screenshot265.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img15.hostingpics.net/pics/405678screenshot265.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.hostingpics.net/viewer.php?id=908998screenshot266.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img15.hostingpics.net/pics/908998screenshot266.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022908998screenshot266.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cs